 also serves as a versatile coffee base for you to customise and create other versions of kopi. Whether it includes adding a little sugar or milk, you can create a cup of kopi to your liking with ease. Certified with a Healthier Choice symbol by the Health Promotion Board, the OWL Kopi-O Kosong is made up of freshly ground coffee and does not contain sugar. Caring for your vision is important as it affects your quality of life. Kinohimits­u EyeBright Powder is a scientific­ally advanced eye care formula that supports overall vision and protects your eye tissue through a proprietar­y blend of antioxidan­ts. It contains high quality patented FloraGLO® Lutein, a highly bioavailab­le natural source of lutein extracted from marigold flowers. The formula is carefully tailored to meet the needs of your eyes from childhood to golden age and it is also suitable for vegetarian­s to consume. Kinohimits­u From 15 – 31 July 2020, you can get 2 months’ supply of with a free eye exam voucher at just $65.90 on Kinohimits­u’s official is also available on Qoo10, Lazada, Shopee, EyeBright
